title: Bob, The Galactic Bum (01 - 04) (1995)
description:
Bob, The Galactic Bum (01 - 04) (1995) 


The Creators owned the rights to Bob the Galactic Bum, but the initial series took place in the DC Universe with Lobo and other LEGION guest stars. This meant that when the comic was reprinted in the pages of Judge Dredd Megazine, the DC characters were replaced with substitutes (Lobo became a large lesbian named Asbo for example).
